            <h4 class="advantage-title">能力输出</h4>
            <p class="advantage-desc">大数据服务先驱探索企业（咨询、规划、落地）</p>
          </div>

          <div class="advantage-card fade-in" data-delay="400">
            <div class="advantage-number orange">04</div>
            <h4 class="advantage-title">全过程保障</h4>
